    <p class="abp">This website was created by <a href="https://royceandrew.github.io/" target="_blank">Royce Andrew</a>, who knows firsthand the power of laughter and the importance of not taking life too seriously. With this blog, Andrew aims to create a community where we can all embrace our most embarrassing moments, learn to laugh at ourselves, and find comfort in the fact that we’re all human.</p>
